# Figma Design System Rules (ACE4KA)

This project follows design specs from **Figma file «В разработку»**. Six key nodes define layout, components, and tokens. Use `FIGMA-NODES.md` and `css/design-tokens.css` as the source of truth; this rule summarizes how to implement them.

## Reference nodes

| Node ID | Scope | Where in code |
|---------|--------|----------------|
| **1-202** | Hero (first screen) | `HomePage` — `.hero`, `.hero__row`, `.hero-content`, `.hero-vector` |
| **1-399** | Projects page layout | `ProjectsPage` — `.page-projects__wrap` |
| **1-522** | Project detail page | `ProjectDetailPage` — `.project-page-wrap`, `.project-detail` |
| **16-184** | Footer area / links row | `Footer` — `.footer-links-row` (or parent of 16-185…) |
| **16-164** | Header | `Header` — `.header`, `.nav`, `.nav-list`, `.logo`, `.lang-switch` |
| **16-170** | Footer | `Footer` — `.footer`, `.footer-ace4ka`, `.footer-inner` |

## Tokens to use

- **Colors:** `css/design-tokens.css` and `:root` in `css/style.css`: `--color-bg`, `--color-text`, `--color-surface`, `--color-text-muted`, `--color-text-extra-muted`, `--font-body`.
- **Spacing:** Prefer `--space-8`, `--space-16`, `--space-24`, `--space-48`, `--space-64` from design-tokens; section gaps 64px (hero→projects), 48px (projects grid), 24px (cards).
- **Typography:** Inter only. Use `var(--font-body)`. Sizes: 12px labels/uppercase, 14px nav/links, 18–24px body/lead, 60px project title, 96px hero title; letter-spacing from Figma (e.g. -1px, 0.55px, 0.6px).
- **Radii:** 8px default (`--radius`), 16px cards, 21px hero images, 9999px pills.
- **Effects:** `--mix-blend-exclusion` for logo/lang; `--shadow-nav-active` for active nav pill; `backdrop-filter: blur(12px)` for nav pill and active state.

## Component rules by node

### 1-202 Hero
- Max content width 896px (or 1290px container); hero + card row gap 12px; section gap below 64px.
- Role/label: 14px, 20px line-height, letter-spacing 1px, 60% opacity.
- H1: 96px, 96px line-height, -6px letter-spacing.
- Lead/description: 24px, max-width 661px.
- Info grid: label 12px/16px, 1px tracking, 40% opacity; value 18px/28px -1px.
- Use `data-node-id="1-202"` on hero container when implementing.

### 1-399 Projects page
- Top offset 152px (or padding); gap 48px to grid.
- Logo section: title + filter pills; grid 1290px, row-gap 24px, column-gap 8px.
- Cards max 639px; image 16:9, radius 16px.
- Use `data-node-id="1-399"` on `.page-projects__wrap`.

### 1-522 Project detail page
- Background `#0a0a0a` (`.main--project`).
- Back link: 14px, 0.55px letter-spacing, uppercase.
- Hero image: 1310×721px, border-radius 21px.
- Top row: title+lead (left, max ~863px) | meta card (right, 415px, #0f0f0f, 16px radius, 24px padding).
- Grid: 2 cols, gap 24px; cards #0f0f0f, 16px radius, 33px padding; label 12px 0.6px uppercase 40%; body 18px 29.25px -0.44px 80%.
- Footer row: border-top #262626, padding-top 65px; 2 cols gap 48px; tools pills 12px border #262626; links 14px underline.
- Use `data-node-id="1-522"` on `.project-page-wrap` and child node IDs per FIGMA-NODES.md.

### 16-184 (Footer area)
- Part of footer; links row or container for 16-185…16-209. Use `.footer-links-row`, gap 14px, 14px uppercase links.

### 16-164 Header (master 1-230; live instance **300:107467**)
- Padding 21px; min-height 88px; max-width 1358px.
- Logo: 24px, 32px line-height, -1px, #fafafa, mix-blend-mode: exclusion; non-breaking space in «Ася Олейниченко».
- Nav pill (300:107467): background rgba(255,255,255,0.11), padding 4px, border-radius 9999px, `backdrop-filter` via **`--blur-nav-list`** (liquid blur) + saturate; **inline-flex**, **gap 8px**, **justify-content: flex-start**; links inside pill use **normal** mix-blend so blur reads; active link rgba(0,0,0,0.55), inset box-shadow, **outline 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.2)**, optional blur on active (`--blur-nav-pill`).
- Active link: background rgba(0,0,0,0.55), border rgba(255,255,255,0.48), letter-spacing 1px, inset shadow per `--shadow-nav-active`.
- Lang: 24px, min-width 228px, mix-blend exclusion.
- Use `data-node-id="300:107467"` on `.header` (see `Header.jsx`); master frame remains [1-230](https://www.figma.com/design/3p1Mnu6yIL6Y8CwebsdP1F/%D0%92-%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%B7%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%B1%D0%BE%D1%82%D0%BA%D1%83?node-id=1-230&m=dev).

### 16-170 Footer
- Max-width 1358px. ACE4KA block (home only): 20.625rem, 600, #fff, -webkit-text-stroke 78px #101010; then inner block #101010, 16px padding.
- Status row: dot 19px, text 24px 1.2 -1px; links row gap 14px, 14px uppercase; note 24px max-width 661px.
- Use `data-node-id="16-170"` and child node IDs on footer elements.

## Implementation checklist

1. **New components:** Add `data-node-id` matching Figma when the component maps to a known node; list new nodes in `FIGMA-NODES.md`.
2. **Styles:** Prefer `css/design-tokens.css` variables; add new tokens there when a value repeats or comes from Figma.
3. **No Tailwind:** Use plain CSS in `css/style.css` (or component-scoped); do not introduce Tailwind unless the project adds it.
4. **Figma link:** File — [В разработку](https://www.figma.com/design/3p1Mnu6yIL6Y8CwebsdP1F/...?node-id=0-1&m=dev). For any node, open in Dev mode and align spacing, type, and colors with this rule and `FIGMA-NODES.md`.
